---
title: Paprika Chicken and Cherry Tomatoes with green peas and rice
description: One of the best ways to enjoy cherry tomatoes is to heat them until tender and beautifully juicy. Here, the softened tomatoes are stirred into a buttery sauce and served with paprika-spiced chicken, fluffy rice and vibrant green peas for a recipe with an array of exciting elements.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R19_W50_IE_IEQC18296-2_Main_high-c3489afe.jpg
